to get it... I saw lots of other spells in that time.  Mine dropped off a green con wurm we were going to invis past... lucky the warriors invis dropped.</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Roawen</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Sig is correct.<BR>I cant auction in Velks because of the special rule set on Firiona Vie, you can not use the /auction command anywhere but a city zone.<BR>The reason I am starting so early (just gathering information at this stage really... hadnt planned on hunting the wurms till late 30's early 40's) is because of Trivial Loot Code, which is in effect in every zone on FV. I want to make sure I dont tlc the mob that drops it.<BR>There are only two guilds big enough to have this kind of stuff as "hand me downs"... and they are just barely big enough.<BR>Im sure eventually I'll end up buying it  <IMG SRC="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/frown.gif"> but I would at least like to try to camp it, even if it is just once.</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Quotison</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">My friend got his copy for 250pp. I didn't want to pay more then he did for it  <IMG SRC="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/smile.gif"><P>When I was level 40 I kept a lookout in EC for someone selling the spell. I saw someone selling it for 500. <P>Later, I see the same guy selling it for 300. I had 250 in my pocket, and send him a tell asking if he'll send it for that amount. Five minutes later I have celestial healing  <IMG SRC="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/smile.gif"><P>------------------<BR><B><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=42628" TARGET=_blank>Quotison Iachwer</A></B><BR>45th Level Dwarven Cleric<BR>Tarew Marr Server</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Alilinkie</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">LOL I Payed 1k for this spell  <IMG SRC="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/frown.gif"><P>But that was a long time ago.<P>But anyway it drops quite alot from Upper Kobolds in Velks.<P>Hope this helps <P>Alilinkie<BR>58 Templar RN</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>
